snippet.title: Lords of the Fallen - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | Future Games Show 2023
snippet.description:
Lords of the Fallen is a dark fantasy action RPG where players will embark on an epic quest to overthrow Adyr, the demon God. Take a look at the gameplay showcase for Lords of the Fallen launching on October 13 for PlayStation 5, Xbox Series S|X, and PC.

#IGN #Gaming #LordsOfTheFallen
